data.title: Enterprise, UT
data.meta_description: See what it's like to live in Enterprise, UT. Explore reviews and statistics on crime, real estate, and cost of living.
data.text:
Living in Mountain Green is a great place to live because of the beautiful mountains and almost perfect climate in all four seasons. There are plenty of activities to do like mountain biking, hiking, skiing, birding, etc. Thought it's a ski town it's a small ski town where there isn't much development like there could be. It's a small community so word travels fast, it's good and bad because you establish relationships easily but gossip is evident.

There is hardly any crime. But as far as safety you might get injured due to recreational activities you may be involved in.
